Toy USB Keyboard Driver
------------------------------------------

When any USB keyboard is plugged in, this module will be automatically loaded
by the userspace hotplug tools (depmod / kmod / udev / mdev / systemd,
depending on the distribution you are on.)

Compile, load and unload module with (we need this registered early):
# make
# ln -s /path/to/module.ko /lib/modules/`uname -r`
# reboot
